Everonn Plunges by Limit for Third Straight Session, Loses 42%

-- B y   S a n t a n u   C h a k r a b o r t y
-- 
2011-09-06T04:18:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-06/everonn-plunges-by-limit-for-third-straight-session-loses-42-.html
Everonn Education Ltd. (EEDU) , a provider
of educational and training services, fell by the daily limit
for third straight session in Mumbai, losing 42 percent of its
value during the period.  The stock retreated 28 rupees, or 10 percent, to 252.5
rupees at 9:37 a.m., adding to the 20 percent slump yesterday
and on Sept. 2, after the company said Managing Director P.
Kishore was taken into judicial custody.  To contact the reporters on this story:
